    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are 10-year-old Kiet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is 2005, and your brother is dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing to do but play video games.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/6ba6668585e4461357b1e7e70c31dc2f.poster.avif?t=1763004640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/6ba6668585e4461357b1e7e70c31dc2f.webm?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/6ba6668585e4461357b1e7e70c31dc2f.mp4?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >While ignoring your mom and grandparents, you can:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find out why everybody (including your own body) is turning against you in a slice-of-life role-playing game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/5ca991a9af2c132545f1cce2af81b28a.poster.avif?t=1763004640\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/5ca991a9af2c132545f1cce2af81b28a.webm?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/5ca991a9af2c132545f1cce2af81b28a.mp4?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet your late brother’s awful friends in an online first-person shooter as they search for a hidden sex scene.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/aa7b57c5accb5b6f794ceb25ecee17b3.poster.avif?t=1763004640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/aa7b57c5accb5b6f794ceb25ecee17b3.webm?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/aa7b57c5accb5b6f794ceb25ecee17b3.mp4?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/e1b563613a84dcda7e10000db61a1637.poster.avif?t=1763004640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/e1b563613a84dcda7e10000db61a1637.webm?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163660/extras/e1b563613a84dcda7e10000db61a1637.mp4?t=1763004640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
